headline.main: Czar Bust in Crimea Reportedly Appears to Shed Tears
headline.print_headline: Czar Bust in Crimea Reportedly Appears to Shed Tears

lead_paragraph: A British daredevil known for his vertigo-inspiring online videos chronicling his climbs up buildings and construction cranes was interrogated by Dubai police over his recent ascents in the sheikhdom, authorities said Sunday.
